verses.text:
Then David gave to Solomon his son the plans for the porch of
the temple, for its houses, for its treasuries, for its upper rooms, for its inner rooms, for the place
of the mercy seat;

and the plans of all that he had by the Spirit, for the courts of the
LORD’s house, for all the surrounding rooms, for the treasuries of God’s house, and for the treasuries
of the dedicated things;

by weight also for the lamp stands of gold, and for its lamps, of gold,
by weight for every lamp stand and for its lamps; and for the lamp stands of silver, by weight for every
lamp stand and for its lamps, according to the use of every lamp stand;
